For me, it downloaded with cantera.  Are you on a windows machine? 
If so, go to:

Start-->Programs-->Cantera-->Documentation

This will open up a folder w/ the pdf in it.  If it's not there, the
sourceforge site calls it 'definingphases.pdf'.  Download here:

http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/cantera/definingphases.pdf?download


~Steven
